    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/cannon-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Cannon Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carina-heights" style="color:#c4912a;">Carina Heights</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carindale" style="color:#c4912a;">Carindale</a>.</p>
